H&R Block Digital Privacy Notice
This H&R Block Digital Privacy Notice (“Notice”) describes how H&R Block, or one of its corporate affiliates, uses personal information collected through:
Our website and online and software tax preparation products and services;
The products and services offered through
HRBlock.com
,
Makeeveryblockbetter.com
, and MyBlock
®
(it does not apply to the websites of
Block Advisors
or
Spruce Money
); and
Our mobile applications that incorporate this Notice.
